 "id": 317064}, "last_reply_by": "CastleBUPT", "last_touched": 1613214763, "title": "安卓手机用超过一年多拍摄录像会卡，怎么解决?", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/753137", "created": 1613179830, "content": "我现在使用的是 Pixel 2XL，之前也用过华为 P10 和 iPhone，很久以前也用过摩托的一款。\n\n\n\n我发现安卓手机用个一年多到两年除了手机会变卡以外，摄像也会卡顿（一分钟的视频会卡一到两次，每次一秒左右），拍出来的视频也是卡帧。而用 iPhone 好像没这个问题。\n\n\n\n这是安卓的普遍现象吗? 除了定期恢复出厂设置有什么办法解决吗?", "content_rendered": "<p>我现在使用的是 Pixel 2XL，之前也用过华为 P10 和 iPhone，很久以前也用过摩托的一款。</p>\n<p>我发现安卓手机用个一年多到两年除了手机会变卡以外，摄像也会卡顿（一分钟的视频会卡一到两次，每次一秒左右），拍出来的视频也是卡帧。而用 iPhone 好像没这个问题。</p>\n<p>这是安卓的普遍现象吗? 除了定期恢复出厂设置有什么办法解决吗?</p>\n", "last_modified": 1613179830, "replies": 36, "id": 753137}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1612151314", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1612151314", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 43179, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1612151314", "stars": 7241, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"username": "ljiaming19", "website": "", "github": "", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7ea13e708a579d5311c0a6190533c3d6?s=24&d=retro", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/ljiaming19", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1476237254, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7ea13e708a579d5311c0a6190533c3d6?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7ea13e708a579d5311c0a6190533c3d6?s=24&d=retro", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 195754}, "last_reply_by": "zeni123", "last_touched": 1613213528, "title": "家用电脑 i7 cpu 可以连续几个星期 100%运行吗", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/753163", "created": 1613195674, "content": "用自己的电脑跑 DFT(密度泛函)计算咪唑分子的能量 大概需要几个星期 cpu 满负荷运行 上次用 DFT 跑了几天就感觉 windows 系统在 cpu 满负荷的时候开始有点不稳定了 有时候打